        {
            "title": "黑期重越兩萬六暫高水逾30點 重磅港股ADR變動不大",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">新加坡黑期於今早約8時18分升32點或0.13%，報26016點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股ADR指數報26021點，較香港上日現貨收市高43點或0.17%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合每股港幣490.4元，較上日香港收市低3.02元或0.61%；阿里巴巴(09988)ADR收市折合每股港幣133元，較上日香港收市高1.24元或0.94%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美團(03690)ADR收市折合每股港幣82.6元，較上日香港收市高0.1元或0.12%；京東(09618)ADR收市折合每股港幣118.6元，較上日香港收市高0.1元或0.08%；小米(01810)ADR收市折合每股港幣31.2元，較上日香港收市低0.03元或0.09%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：騰訊官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滙控(00005)ADR收市折合每股港幣140.6元，較上日香港收市高0.56元或0.4%；友邦(01299)ADR收市折合每股港幣82.1元，較上日香港收市高0.45元或0.55%；港交所(00388)ADR收市折合每股港幣411.5元，較上日香港收市低0.05元或0.01%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國平安(02318)ADR收市折合每股港幣61.4元，較上日香港收市高0.48元或0.79%；建設銀行(00939)ADR收市折合每股港幣8.9元，較上日香港收市低0.02元或0.19%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒指期貨夜市收報26041點，升76點，較上日恒指收市25978點，高水63點。科指期貨夜市收報4926點，較上日科指收市高水24點；國指期貨夜市收報8801點，較上日國指收市高水25點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15925016-%e9%bb%91%e6%9c%9f%e9%87%8d%e8%b6%8a%e5%85%a9%e8%90%ac%e5%85%ad%e6%9a%ab%e9%ab%98%e6%b0%b4%e9%80%be30%e9%bb%9e-%e9%87%8d%e7%a3%85%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1adr%e8%ae%8a%e5%8b%95%e4%b8%8d%e5%a4%a7",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/ADR-1_source-bp_-2-1.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-27 08:23:25",
