            "title": "日韓股市初段再漲 日股曾創新高升幅暫收窄至0.22% 韓股升逾1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">日韓股市今早初段持續向好，日股一度再創新高。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260304_FI_source-ap_KS.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260304_FI_source-ap_KS.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">日經平均指數今早曾衝上60106點，其後升幅迅速收窄，截至香港時間上午約8時12分報59850點，升幅收窄至134點或0.22%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">南韓首爾綜合指數暫升80點或1.25%，報6556點。</p>\n</div>",
